verbose_text: ERK phosphorylation and FOXM1 activity were examined following the downregulation of miR-130b, indicating that there were no signficant changes between the control group and the antagomiR group, both in phosphorylated ERK (1.00 +/-0.16 vs. 0.95 +/-0.12, P> 0.05) and in FOXM1 expression (1.00 +/-0.13 vs. 1.08 +/-0.16, P> 0.05) (XREF_FIG).
